Package: clmpdashboard
Type: Package
Title: Functions to compile data for MP activity dashboard
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Elise Uberoi
Maintainer: Elise Uberoi <eliseuberoi@gmail.com>
Description: This package enables users to get data on Members' activities in Parliament:
    including their roles on APPGs, the Early Day Motions they sign and the debates they participate in. 
    The package includes functions to join activity data with Member data. 
